.. -*- restructuredtext -*-

===============
Release History
===============

**1.1** (2011-05-04)

    * css media query automatically hides sidebar & trim
      for small displays (eg mobile devices)

    * toggleable sections js code rewritten,
      now auto-expands based on url hash.

    * autodoc_sections extension parser much less fragile,
      relies on fewer assumptions about source.

    * fixed header margin glitch that was occurring under chrome.

    * various minor layout enhancements

**1.0** (2011-03-25)

    First public release.
